Installation
------------

UNIX-like systems:

cd ~/.vim

unzip /path/to/gedim.zip

vi
:helptags ~/.vim/doc


Windows systems:

Unpack the .zip file and copy the files to your
gvim or vim configuration directory, then:

vi
:helptags /path/to/doc


